OL,3,CMajorca and Menorca struck by heavy
OL,4,Cflooding, leaving train passengers
OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FThe Spanish island of Majorca has been
OL,8,Finundated by heavy floods, causing
OL,9,Fflight delays and stranding passengers
OL,10,Fon a train stuck on submerged rails.
OL,12,FEmergency services reported carrying
OL,13,Fout dozens of rescues and attending
OL,14,Fincidents including fires started by
OL,15,Flightning strikes.
OL,17,FFirefighters said they had to rescue
OL,18,F29 passengers from the Palma-Manacor
OL,19,Ftrain line near Petra, after the train
OL,20,Fwas brought to a standstill by
OL,21,Ffloodwaters. No injuries were reported.
