OL,5,Cstranded
OL,7,FFlooding in neighbouring island
OL,8,FMenorca was also reported on Thursday,
OL,9,Fwith witnesses taking to social media
OL,10,Fto post footage of roads submerged by
OL,11,Fsurging water.
OL,13,FSpain's Military Emergencies Unit
OL,14,Fannounced it had travelled to Majorca
OL,15,Fto support local authorities.
OL,17,FThe country's meteorological service
OL,18,Fissued several warnings for heavy
OL,19,Fshowers and storms throughout Majorca
OL,20,Fon Thursday.
