OL,7,FNorth and north-east regions were on
OL,8,Fred alert for very heavy rain until
OL,9,F3pm, with forecasts predicting up to
OL,10,F180 litres of water per square metre
OL,11,Fto accumulate within four or five
OL,12,Fhours.
